</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Sattelbog<ex>er</ex></expan>, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> gar oft und vil
                                ver<expan>schribe<ex>n</ex></expan> und gemant, zu
                                <expan>laist<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Perching von Hilpolt
                                Frawn<expan>berg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als ir an <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>brief<ex>en</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> habt,
                        daz uns aber noch bisher niht <expan>gehelff<ex>en</ex></expan> mag, daz ir
                        uns ewr insigel <expan>halt<ex>en</ex></expan> und dem gnug sein wellet, des
                        ir ewch gen uns <pb facs="#facs_252" id="126r"/><expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        habt, des wir uns zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sehen</expan>
                        hetten. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir unczher
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> geschont, daz wir uns des von ewch niht
                        beklagt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan> ewch <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mit
                        disem brief, ir haltt uns und schikt noch
                                <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ewr knecht und
                        pferd in <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Windisch hawse gen Perching,
                                <expan>daselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zu <expan>laist<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von <expan>pferd<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>pferd<ex>en</ex></expan>, uns
                        darausz niht zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> nach
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>schuldbr<ex>iefs</ex></expan> sag, bis wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> schulde beczalt
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Wan tett ir des niht, so
                                <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir uns des hinfür von ewch
                                <expan>erklag<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
